  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="DA">Empowerment of survivors of 1980s Massacres in Matabeleland, Zimbabwe to take part in truth telling outreach through the National Peace &amp; Reconciliation Commission</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="DA">The objective is to empower and emotionally support women/men of two Matabeleland Provinces, Zimbabwe in taking advantage of the truth telling outreach of the National Peace and Reconciliation Commission, to place the history of the &#x2018;Gukurahundi&#x2019; massacres of the 1980s into the national historical record, thereby promoting the integration of victims into the Zimbabwe body politick.</narrative>
  </description>
